## Current Conclusion

1. Merge to `main` triggers CI; wait for green build.
2. Run `<deploy-command>` against staging; smoke-test the three critical
   paths (list them, don't rely on memory of what they are).
3. If staging passes, promote the same build artifact to production â€” do
   not rebuild, to guarantee staging and production ran identical code.
4. Tag the release in version control immediately after promotion.

